flowchart TD
    Start([User Input]) --> Form[CreateGoalForm Component]
    Form --> Validate{Validate with Zod Schema}
    Validate -->|Invalid| ShowErrors[Show Errors]
    ShowErrors --> UserFixes[User Fixes]
    UserFixes --> Validate
    Validate -->|Valid| Optimistic[Optimistic Update to Store]
    Optimistic --> DispatchPending[Dispatch: createGoalPending]
    DispatchPending --> AddTemp[Store: Add temporary goal with loading state]
    AddTemp --> APIService[API Service: createGoal]
    APIService --> Transform[Transform data to API format]
    Transform --> ConvertDates[Convert dates to ISO strings]
    ConvertDates --> SetDefaults[Set defaults: progress: 0, timestamps]
    SetDefaults --> RemoveFields[Remove client-only fields]
    RemoveFields --> HTTPRequest[HTTP Request: POST /api/goals]
    HTTPRequest --> Backend[Backend API Handler]
    Backend --> ServerValidate{Validate with Zod Schema}
    ServerValidate -->|Invalid| Return400[Return 400 with errors]
    Return400 --> ErrorHandler[API Service: Handle Error]
    ServerValidate -->|Valid| Authorize{Authorize: Check user permissions}
    Authorize -->|Unauthorized| Return403[Return 403]
    Return403 --> ErrorHandler
    Authorize -->|Authorized| Generate[Generate: id UUID, createdAt, updatedAt]
    Generate --> SetDefaults2[Set defaults: progress: 0, progressHistory: [], notes: [], attachments: [], relatedGoals: []]
    SetDefaults2 --> Database[Database: INSERT Goal]
    Database --> Transaction[Transaction: Insert goal record]
    Transaction --> InsertMain[Insert main goal fields]
    InsertMain --> InsertMilestones{Has milestones?}
    InsertMilestones -->|Yes| InsertMilestoneData[Insert milestones]
    InsertMilestoneData --> InsertProgress
    InsertMilestones -->|No| InsertProgress[Insert initial progress entry]
    InsertProgress --> ReturnCreated[Return: Created goal with all fields]
    ReturnCreated --> APIResponse[API Response: 201 Created]
    APIResponse --> TransformResponse[API Service: Transform Response]
    TransformResponse --> ConvertDates2[Convert dates from ISO strings to Date objects]
    ConvertDates2 --> AddComputed[Add computed fields if needed]
    AddComputed --> UpdateStore[State Management: Update Store]
    UpdateStore --> DispatchSuccess[Dispatch: createGoalSuccess]
    DispatchSuccess --> RemoveTemp[Remove temporary goal]
    RemoveTemp --> AddReal[Add real goal to store]
    AddReal --> UpdateCache[Update goal list cache]
    UpdateCache --> UpdateUI[UI Component: Update View]
    UpdateUI --> ShowSuccess[Show success message]
    ShowSuccess --> Navigate[Navigate to goal detail page OR Add goal to list view]
    Navigate --> ClearForm[Clear form if staying on page]
    ClearForm --> End([Goal Created Successfully])
    
    ErrorHandler --> ParseError[Parse error response]
    ParseError --> ErrorType{Error Type?}
    ErrorType -->|400| ExtractFieldErrors[Extract field errors]
    ErrorType -->|403| PermissionError[Show permission error]
    ErrorType -->|500| GenericError[Show generic error]
    ErrorType -->|Network| NetworkError[Show network error]
    ExtractFieldErrors --> ErrorState[State Management: Error Handling]
    PermissionError --> ErrorState
    GenericError --> ErrorState
    NetworkError --> ErrorState
    ErrorState --> DispatchError[Dispatch: createGoalError]
    DispatchError --> RemoveTemp2[Remove temporary goal]
    RemoveTemp2 --> SetError[Set error state]
    SetError --> DisplayError[UI Component: Display Error]
    DisplayError --> ShowErrorMsg[Show error message]
    ShowErrorMsg --> ShowFieldErrors[Show field-level errors if validation]
    ShowFieldErrors --> AllowRetry[Allow user to retry or cancel]
    AllowRetry --> EndError([Error Handled])

    style Start fill:#e1f5ff
    style End fill:#c8e6c9
    style EndError fill:#ffcdd2
    style Validate fill:#fff9c4
    style ServerValidate fill:#fff9c4
    style Authorize fill:#fff9c4
    style ErrorType fill:#fff9c4

